title: Cypress Restaurant
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Upscale Southern American regional-style restaurant in a casual setting. Vegan items include "the Cypress vegan," a chickpea & smoked mushroom turnover with curried coconut sauce; and mango-chile pepper chutney. The eggplant bruschetta is vegetarian but can be modified by request. Additional soup and salad offerings can be requested as vegan. Reservations suggested.
